[Java convert octal to decimal](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/octal-to-decimal-java/)

Java convert octal to decimal

To convert octal to decimal use parseInt() method of Integer class. Syntax for Integer.parseInt() method is as follows

public static int parseInt(String s, int radix) throws NumberFormatException

public class OctalToDecimalDemo
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      String strOctal = "141";
      // converting octal to decimal number using Integer.parseInt() method
      int decimal = Integer.parseInt(strOctal, 8);
      System.out.println(decimal);
   }
}


Output:

97
